# The IFC binaries are sourced from public assets at deploy time — see
# PROVENANCE.md — and not committed. The two design-doc PDFs ARE committed
# because they're rendered from the .md sources next to them via
# render_pdfs.py and they're the actual demo content; any other PDF
# dropped into docs/ stays ignored as a safety net.

*.ifc
docs/*.pdf
docs/*.PDF

# Allow:
!README.md
!PROVENANCE.md
!.gitignore
!embeddings.json
!docs/architectural-design-brief.pdf
!docs/structural-design-statement.pdf
